														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2831682">
									

<ul>
<li>Self-insert characters/ Mary Sues. We get it, you want to create a scip that personifies yourself. But that doesn't mean that it has to be the best at everything (e.g. the strongest, the smartest, the most badass, the unkillable). That doesn't mean you can't make a self-insert, but you should write it with a well thought out story.</li>
</ul>

