														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2831720">
									

<ul>
<li>Anything that is evil for absolutely no reason. By this, I mean it attacked researchers just because they showed up, and it will kill any form of life it comes across. SCP-682 is a good example of this.</li>
<li>Portal to another dimension.</li>
<li>Object/organism that makes you go insane for no apparent reason. Just being around it or handling it makes you go insane. (Insanity has become a rather overused cliche in horror, so I'd suggest we find something new.)</li>
</ul>

